dct_title_s: Peta daerah bahaya Gunung Merapi, Jawa Tengah / Volcanic hazard map, Merapi Volcano, central Java / by L. Pardyanto [and others].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Also covers Yogyakarta city region. Includes text, notes, glossary, and location map. Location map and colophon on envelope.
